<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://englishrussia.com/2007/12/19/adopted-russian-kids/" title="8:40 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">December 19, 2007</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://englishrussia.com/author/" title="View all posts by "></a></span></span>
