<p><!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd"><br />
<html><body>
<p><img src="http://englishrussia.com/images/adopted_kids/1.jpg" alt="adopted Russian kids 1"></p>
<p></p>
<p>These photos don&#8217;t need comments. These are photos of Russian kids adopted from &#8220;children&#8217;s home&#8221; the worst place for a kid to be. They get there a budget of $100/mo for each kid, they don&#8217;t have toys they don&#8217;t have love of parents it&#8217;s sad and that&#8217;s great that there are people even in Russia who can adopt and save kids.</p>
<p>All the photos are in &#8220;Before and After&#8221; manner, you can easily tell where is the &#8220;before&#8221; photo.</p>
<p><span id="more-1697"></span><br />
<br />
<hr />

