Russia is pushing for foster care and for their own people to adopt but it is so looked down on still.<br />
There are 700,000 orphans in Russia &#8211; 75% of those who are not adopted do not live to the age of 25.<br />
It is nothing against Russia &#8211; every country has children who need parents.</p>

