		<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-224514">
				<div id="div-comment-224514" class="comment-body">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<cite class="fn">D</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://englishrussia.com/2007/12/19/adopted-russian-kids/#comment-224514">
			December 20, 2007 at 12:59 pm</a>		</div>

		<p>Sad. Its not the kids fault.</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2007/12/19/adopted-russian-kids/?replytocom=224514#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-224514", "224514", "respond", "1697")'>Reply</a>		</div>
